    "The \"Adoption paths\" cluster focuses on various aspects of digital transformation in small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs), while the \"Business model\" cluster emphasizes the crucial role of transforming current business models.",
    "The keyword Burst Analysis provides insights into the chronological development of prominent research areas.",
